        "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review+1\n\nit used to be use by VNFSDK and I know that a vCPE Tosca was also using CLI\nbut I am not sure it is very active (according t github insights=\nThe only test is a healthcheck test (check readiness/liveness) but there are not E2E tests dealing with CLI\n\nI added some people in review\nif not comment I assume we could merge",
